	It's news to me that these are the estimates for the relative 
effectiveness in ozone-layer depletion.  But, supposing for the sake 
of argument that it is so, the answer is of course the solid moral 
principle that two wrongs don't make a right.

>
><<I am not a tree hugger. But releasing R12 into the atmosphere is both
>illegal and has an adverse effect on mother earth.>>
